{
  "stem": "293.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Alexandrovich, a dear friend of mine, MD doctor, that he, his wife, and his child, Mila and I will go with the sewers out because he already make arrangement with friends to accepted us, you see?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he went earlier because the-- the-- the segregation start in his area sooner than in ours.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the-- you know, they did section by section.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he went to the sewers, and he was one of the few who really got out early in the morning from the sewers, and they disappear in the city.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I came in to look for them-- I was thinking that they still there-- and I left Mila in apartment.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was very scared, and I was scared.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was scared in this time, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I come back, when I found out that they already went to sewers and already were killing people in the sewers, you see?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went for Mila.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I came over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's no Mila there anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I start to looking in the hospital because there were about 60, 70, body laying there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or maybe she-- she got killed or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then somebody told me that they saw Mila going with a group of Madritsch-- because she was working for Madritsch-- to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I decide to hide because I figured out when I got out, I can be much more of help for her than being inside with her.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was lucky I came out with life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was one of the last one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The group was maybe about 25, 30 people who were supposed to clean something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after when this group left, ghetto was sealed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Close to 7,000 people was killed over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is a very difficult question to answer.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
